shed datasets were used:</p><p><element-citation id="dataset3" publication-type="data" specific-use="references"><person-group person-group-type="author"><collab>Reaves BJ et al</collab></person-group><year iso-8601-date="2017">2017</year><source>The effect on anthelmintic drugs on Brugia malayi gene expression in vivo</source><ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/bioproject/PRJNA388112">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/bioproject/PRJNA388112</ext-link><comment>SRA BioProject, PRJNA388112</comment></element-citation></p></sec><supplementary-material><ext-link xlink:href="elife-83100-supp-v1.zip">Download zip</ext-link><p>Any figures and tables for this article are included in the PDF. The zip folder contains additional supplemental files.</p></supplementary-material></sec></back></article>